### ProductsService API Tests

### 1. Get all products (public endpoint - no authentication required)
GET https://localhost:7002/products
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get product by ID (protected endpoint - requires authentication)
GET https://localhost:7002/products/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json

### 3. Create new product (protected endpoint - requires authentication)
POST https://localhost:7002/products
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "New Laptop",
    "description": "High-performance gaming laptop",
    "price": 1299.99,
    "category": "Electronics"
}

### 4. Get specific product by ID
GET https://localhost:7002/products/2
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json

### Note: Replace YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE with actual JWT token from UsersService login
